dmenu-highlight-4.9.diff
dmenu-numbers-4.9.diff
dmenu-center-20200111-8cd37e1.diff
dmenu-mousesupport-4.9.diff
dmenu-borderoption-20200217-bf60a1e.diff
dmenu-password-4.9.diff

Options
-------
-bw     - defines the border width
          echo 'item1\nitem2\nitem3' | dmenu -bw 3

